msgctxt "seo_title"
msgid "Plan Your Trip | Mozilla Festival 2026"
msgstr "Planen Sie Ihre Reise | Mozilla Festival 2026"

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid "Planning to join MozFest 2026 in Barcelona? Find travel tips, visa support, transport routes, and exclusive hotel deals for this year’s festival at Fabra i Coats."
msgstr "Planen Sie, am MozFest 2026 in Barcelona teilzunehmen? Finden Sie Reisetipps, Visa-Unterstützung, Transportwege und exklusive Hotelangebote für das diesjährige Festival bei Fabra i Coats."

msgctxt "title"
msgid "Plan Your Trip"
msgstr "Planen Sie Ihre Reise"

msgctxt "hero_title"
msgid "Plan Your Trip to Mozilla Festival 2026"
msgstr "Planen Sie Ihre Reise zum Mozilla Festival 2026"

msgctxt "hero_description"
msgid "Joining us in Barcelona? Here are travel tips to help you get ready."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "hero_image_alt_text"
msgid "Barcelona skyline at sunset, with the spires of Barcelona Cathedral and the Sagrada Família rising above dense rooftops, hills behind."
msgstr "Die Skyline von Barcelona bei Sonnenuntergang, mit den Türmen der Kathedrale von Barcelona und der Sagrada Família, die sich über dichten Dächern und Hügeln erhebt."

msgctxt "body.6edde3ab-4317-402c-85ac-82f59f5a5464.title"
msgid "Key Information"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.title"
msgid "Visa Requirements"
msgstr "Visabestimmungen"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.content.ffa9c5b9-4f82-41a7-93c6-c143901c4c8f"
msgid ""
"<b>Prior to booking travel, we recommend you</b> <a id=\"a1\"><b>check if you need a visa to enter Spain</b></a>, or consider booking refundable travel and accommodation to give yourself "
"flexibility."
msgstr ""
"<b>Vor der Buchung Ihrer Reise empfehlen wir Ihnen,</b> <a id=\"a1\"><b>zu überprüfen, ob Sie ein Visum für die Einreise nach Spanien benötigen</b></a>oder eine stornierbare Reise und Unterkunft zu "
"buchen, um sich Flexibilität zu bewahren."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.content.ffa9c5b9-4f82-41a7-93c6-c143901c4c8f"
msgid ""
"For Spain, your passport is always required and must be valid for up to three months after the expected date of departure from the Schengen area, and must have been issued within the previous 10 "
"years to the date of entry."
msgstr ""
"Für Spanien ist Ihr Reisepass immer erforderlich und muss bis zu drei Monate nach dem voraussichtlichen Datum der Ausreise aus dem Schengen-Raum gültig sein und innerhalb der letzten 10 Jahre bis "
"zum Datum der Einreise ausgestellt worden sein."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.content.ffa9c5b9-4f82-41a7-93c6-c143901c4c8f"
msgid "<b>Once you know you are attending Mozilla Festival, we advise you to book your visa appointments as soon as possible</b>, as these can take some time to secure and delay the process."
msgstr ""
"<b>Sobald Sie wissen, dass Sie am Mozilla Festival teilnehmen, empfehlen wir Ihnen, Ihre Visa-Termine so schnell wie möglich zu vereinbaren</b>, da diese einige Zeit in Anspruch nehmen können und "
"den Prozess verzögern könnten."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d1964797-8efe-43dc-931e-d1e9f014fdc9.content.ffa9c5b9-4f82-41a7-93c6-c143901c4c8f"
msgid "If you have questions on the process please contact <a id=\"a1\">festival@mozillafoundation.org</a>"
msgstr "Wenn Sie Fragen zum Prozess haben, wenden Sie sich bitte an <a id=\"a1\">festival@mozillafoundation.org</a>"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.title"
msgid "Travel to Barcelona"
msgstr "Reise nach Barcelona"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid "We advise you to book your travel and accommodation as soon as possible to take advantage of better rates."
msgstr "Wir empfehlen Ihnen, Ihre Reise und Unterkunft so schnell wie möglich zu buchen, um von besseren Preisen zu profitieren."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid "By Air"
msgstr "Mit dem Flugzeug"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid "Barcelona-El Prat Airport (BCN) is the city’s main international airport, offering direct flights from major global destinations."
msgstr "Der Flughafen Barcelona-El Prat (BCN) ist der wichtigste internationale Flughafen der Stadt und bietet Direktflüge von wichtigen globalen Zielen an."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid "By Train"
msgstr "Mit dem Zug"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid "Spain’s high-speed rail network links Barcelona to major European cities, with direct trains from Paris arriving in 6 and a half hours."
msgstr "Spaniens Hochgeschwindigkeitsbahnnetz verbindet Barcelona mit europäischen Großstädten; direkte Züge aus Paris kommen in 6,5 Stunden an."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid ""
"More information on travelling to Spain is available on the <a id=\"a1\">Spanish Tourist Board</a> website. You can also find a list of Spanish consulates and embassies on the <a "
"id=\"a2\">Ministerio de Asuntos Exteriores, Unión Europea y Cooperación</a> website."
msgstr ""
"Weitere Informationen über Reisen nach Spanien finden Sie auf der Website <a id=\"a1\">des spanischen Tourismusverbandes</a>. Eine Liste der spanischen Konsulate und Botschaften finden Sie auch auf "
"der Website des <a id=\"a2\">Ministerio de Asuntos Exteriores, Unión Europea y Cooperación</a>."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.fb0ecea0-a4be-4d3f-8a8a-0700ac7512ed.content.f7082bcb-2ac6-4df1-919f-77b1eddf0d63"
msgid "See hotel suggestions below"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.title"
msgid "Getting around Barcelona"
msgstr "Unterwegs in Barcelona"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid ""
"Barcelona has an excellent public transport network covering metro, bus, tram, and suburban rail. <b>The venue is accessible by local train, metro and buses. The closest station is Sant "
"Andreu</b>,<b> served by the L1 (Red Line), R2, R2N, R11 as well as regional services.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Barcelona verfügt über ein hervorragendes öffentliches Verkehrsnetz, das U-Bahn, Bus, Straßenbahn und S-Bahn abdeckt. <b>Der Veranstaltungsort ist mit dem Nahverkehrszug, der U-Bahn und Bussen "
"erreichbar. Die nächstgelegene Haltestelle ist Sant Andreu,</b>,<b> bedient von der L1 (Rote Linie), R2, R2N, R11 sowie regionalen Verbindungen.</b>"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "Tickets and travel cards"
msgstr "Tickets und Reisekarten"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "<a id=\"a1\"><b>T-casual</b></a><b>:</b> 10 single rides on metro, bus, tram, and FGC trains within Zone 1 which covers the venue and central Barcelona. This is not valid on airport transfers"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "<a id=\"a1\"><b>Hola Barcelona Travel Card</b></a><b>:</b> unlimited travel for 2, 3, 4, or 5 consecutive days. Includes airport transfers on the metro"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "Note that special fares can apply for airport transfers, always check that your ticket is valid before travelling to or from the airport."
msgstr "Beachten Sie, dass für Flughafentransfers Sondertarife gelten können. Überprüfen Sie immer, ob Ihr Ticket gültig ist, bevor Sie zum oder vom Flughafen reisen."

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "Navigation apps"
msgstr "Navigations-Apps"

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "<a id=\"a1\"><b>TMB App</b></a><b>:</b> Barcelona’s official public transport app for live metro, bus, and tram information"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.1ba8d0e3-444c-4694-839f-7918e5eed484.content.6e8ed539-7581-46ba-a775-7fcb24935ff4"
msgid "<a id=\"a1\"><b>Citymapper</b></a><b>:</b> Real time information and routes for public transport, taxis, cycling and walking across Barcelona"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.title"
msgid "Accessibility, Inclusion &amp; Wellbeing"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid ""
"We want Mozilla Festival to be welcoming, navigable, and as safe as possible for all — across all genders, sexualities, faiths, abilities, and backgrounds. We have been working closely with the "
"venue and our production team to plan for the following:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid ""
"A <b>marked accessible route</b> runs through the campus, avoiding cobblestoned areas. The full route map will be published ahead of the festival. By mobility scooter, the longest journey across the"
" venue takes about 4 minutes, and the nearest metro station is about 3 minutes away"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "<b>Elevators are available in all main festival buildings</b> and have been tested for mobility device user access and control"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "Most <b>restrooms at the venue are gender neutral</b>. Accessible restrooms are also available and will be marked on the venue map"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "A <b>quiet space away from high traffic areas</b> with comfortable seating and designated as fragrance-free"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "A <b>multi-faith space</b> for anyone who wishes to observe faith-based customs during the festival"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "A <b>first aid station</b> staffed by trained medical professionals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid "If you have access needs we should know about or questions you'd like to talk through, please email <a id=\"a1\">festival@mozillafoundation.org</a> in advance so we can plan with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.d11ef0ad-7fe2-4e55-9c4c-b42a8d3380c9.content.79081ddd-cb5f-4da8-910c-51d054f5b32c"
msgid ""
"Our Safety Team will be on hand throughout the venue to handle any reports of <b>Community Participation Guidelines</b> violations. You can contact them confidentially at any information point, or "
"by calling a dedicated reporting number that will be shared closer to the event."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.80800d82-fabe-435c-bd67-ebe1b00c3571.title"
msgid "Travel Support"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.80800d82-fabe-435c-bd67-ebe1b00c3571.content.a5a2ea44-ab21-4a34-b7f6-8f7838cd07ef"
msgid ""
"A limited travel fund is available for session hosts whose session proposals are accepted through our Call for Proposals. <b>We are unable to offer travel support for general participants or "
"volunteers.</b>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.80800d82-fabe-435c-bd67-ebe1b00c3571.content.a5a2ea44-ab21-4a34-b7f6-8f7838cd07ef"
msgid ""
"If you have an idea for a session, we encourage you to submit a proposal even if you don't currently have travel funding lined up. Travel support is reviewed as part of the selection process and "
"session hosts who need support can request it then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c9a43f8c-a0b3-4360-a2c5-b5538500b123.tabs.80800d82-fabe-435c-bd67-ebe1b00c3571.content.a5a2ea44-ab21-4a34-b7f6-8f7838cd07ef"
msgid "Please note that funds are limited and support is not guaranteed for every accepted facilitator."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid "Where we'll be"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid "Mozilla Festival 2026 will be held at Recinte Fabra i Coats, Barcelona, Spain, from October 28-30 ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid ""
"Originally built in the nineteenth century as a textile factory, today the Recinte Fabra i Coats precinct houses an institution dedicated to the research, production, exhibition and dissemination of"
" contemporary artistic practices."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid "Located in the Sant Andreu, a formerly independent village in the norther part of Barcelona, it’s easy to reach by metro, bus, or taxi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid ""
"It retains its industrial vibe with a mix of historic, narrow and winding streets filled with independent and boutique stores as well as attractions including the Church of Sant Andreu de Palomar "
"and the Antoni Gaudí designed mosaic floor at Sant Pacià Church."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.left_column.ed486685-ca31-4510-8268-33285747731e"
msgid "<b>Address:<br/></b><i>Carrer de Sant Adrià, Sant Andreu, 08030 Barcelona, Spain</i>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.975f2854-4f06-41d2-a968-6e21ecfb3d09.right_column.08a8a99a-5861-417e-90fb-1b61c0a816c9.image.alt_text"
msgid "Fabra i Coats: brick industrial buildings with a tall chimney and graffiti, under a blue sky."
msgstr "Fabra i Coats: Backstein-Industriegebäude mit hohem Schornstein und Graffiti unter blauem Himmel."

msgctxt "body.b39a2a30-e463-4603-8dca-b8f275634fe7"
msgid "Where to stay"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.b39a2a30-e463-4603-8dca-b8f275634fe7"
msgid "There's a wide range of accommodation across the city to suit all budgets, but we advise you <b>book early</b> as rates can go up as summer approaches."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.b39a2a30-e463-4603-8dca-b8f275634fe7"
msgid "We've partnered with a selection of hotels close to the venue to offer Mozilla Festival attendees special rates. Take a look at the participating hotels below:"
msgstr ""
"Wir haben uns mit einer Auswahl von Hotels in der Nähe des Veranstaltungsortes zusammengetan, um Mozilla Festival-Teilnehmern Sondertarife anzubieten. Werfen Sie einen Blick auf die untenstehenden "
"teilnehmenden Hotels:"

